overview:
San Diego Personal Injury Attorneys is a legal firm specializing in personal injury cases: car accidents, truck accidents, slip and fall, animal bites, medical malpractices, wrongful deaths, and more.

Every one of our attorneys received and maintains a high level degree in the following professional organizations: The California Bar Association, The American Bar Association, and Consumer Attorneys of America. With more than 25 years of experience, we helped recover millions of dollars in damages through the various amount personal injury cases we have worked with.
